data.description: This 4 bdrm, 3.5 bath, 3,388 sq. ft. home sits on 53.5 acres of lush countryside. On the main level, you will find the primary bdrm with 2 closets and an ensuite bath, an additional bdrm with a walk-in closet, a hall bathroom, a kitchen, a dining room, a breakfast room, and an oversized laundry room. Off the laundry room you will find a bonus room and half bathroom. The cozy upstairs has 2 bdrm, walk-in closets, a bathroom, and a living area with built-ins. On the grounds, you will find a 1400 sq. ft. detached garage with a full kitchen and bath that can be used as living quarters. There is a pond, pastureland that is cross fenced with a water source, an 40X60 barn with 3 roll up doors, water, electricity, and 2 Priefert horse stalls. Next to this barn are 3 kennels with a water and cleanout drain. Rounding out this property is a 40X20 hay barn, cattle working pens with a chute, as well as a small open area for an arena with a single pole light conveniently located next to the barn.
